Placement Helm Chart
===================

Setup
-----

Vault
-----
You need to create a secret in vault with the following keys
 * database_connection
 * keystone_password

Refer to the secret in your values

vault:
  settings_secret: secret/data/k8s/<namespace>/placement/settings


Placement settings example:
-----------------
conf:
  keystone_authtoken:
    www_authenticate_uri=https://keystone:5000
    auth_type=password
    memcached_servers=mc1:11211,mc2:11211
    auth_url=https://keystone:5000
    username=placement
    user_domain_name=default
    project_name=service
    project_domain_name=default
    service_token_roles_required=True
    service_type=placement
